<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10376648>
    dc:description "FIGURES 142–147. Phaeoxantha (P.) cruciata cruciata (Brullé), from Argentina,; 142—habitus, ♂; 17,5 mm, Corrientes, LT (MNHN); 143—labels of the LT; 144–145—mandibles: 144—♂, Entre Rios (CCJM); 145—♀, Buenos Aires (CCJM); 146–147—labrum: 146—♂, Entre Rios (CCJM); 147—♀, Buenos Aires (CCJM). Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10376648/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10376650>
    dc:description "FIGURES 148–150. Phaeoxantha (P.) c. cruciata (Brullé), from Argentina (CCJM). 148—habitus, ♂, 16 mm, Entre Rios; 149—ditto, aedeagus; 150—habitus, ♀, 16 mm, Buenos Aires. Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10376650/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10376652>
    dc:description "FIGURES 151–157. Phaeoxantha (P.) c. cruciata (Brullé), from Argentina (CCJM). 151–152—pronotum: 151—♀, Buenos Aires; 152—♂, Entre Rios; 153–157—elytra: 153—♂, Entre Rios; 154—ditto, detail of surface; 155—mutual aspect, ♀, Bue- nos Aires; 156—left elytron, ♀, ibid.; 157—ditto, detail of surface. Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10376652/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10376672>
    dc:description "FIGURES 190–201. Phaeoxantha (P.) bifasciata (Brullé).190–196, 198–201—elytra: 190—♀, Brazil, Teffe (CCJM); 191– 192—ditto, details of surface; 193—♀, Brazil, Rio Solimoes (JWCW); 194–196—Bolivia, Rio Cesarsama (JWCW): 194—♀; 195—♂; 196—ditto, surface detail; 197—♂, aedeagus; 198–201—historical specimens ex Chaudoir (MNHN): 198—♀, as P. bifasciata; 199—ditto, surface detail; 200—♀, as “P. aequinoctialis”; 201—ditto, surface detail. Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10376672/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10376676>
    dc:description "FIGURES 212–220. Phaeoxantha (P.) bifasciata (Brullé), Bolivia. 212—pronotum, ♂, Cabezas (COSJ); 213—ditto, surface detail; 214–218—elytra: 214—♂, Mchareti (COSJ); 215—ditto, surface detail; 216—♀, Buena Vista (JWCW); 217–218—dit- to, surface detail. 219–220—male aedeagus: 219—Mchareti (COSJ); 220—Cabezaz (COSJ); Bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10376676/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

